####Teams

Each box can represent a Team or a person. For the Drawing Office, work allocation is on a 
personal basis, hence each box represents a CAD Operator. The CAD Manager is responsible to keep the incoming box full of recent activities. Any drawing returned with a status which is not A, automatically will be added to his own personal view for allocation.



